Author: VentingFooligan6000
Text: Take some deep breaths in and out and try to relax. That all sounds really delicious and your body can benefit from the nutrients found in that meal. Everyone has days where they eat more than usual and I think a non-disordered person would be able to have that much without a second thought on it.  Please be kind to yourself, let time help you digest your food and make sure you're drinking enough water and properly hydrated. I'm sure you are just fine! Don't punish yourself it will all be okay
